@rules/behavioros-protocol

## 7 Mandatory Steps

| # | Step | Tool | When | Enforcement |
|---|------|------|------|-------------|
| 1 | Select DNA | `bos_select_dna` | Before ANY task | **CRITICAL** — MCP blocks all tools if skipped |
| 2 | Display DNA Block | Visual template | After step 1 | **HIGH** — Human visibility required |
| 3 | Resolve Truth | `bos_resolve_truth` | Before delegating | **CRITICAL** — Delegation blocked if skipped |
| 4 | Create Mission | `create-mission` | Before starting work | **HIGH** — No work without mission ID |
| 5 | Delegate | Task tool | To execute work | **CRITICAL** — Direct execution blocked |
| 6 | Run Audit | `bos_run_audit` | After completion | **CRITICAL** — Mission cannot complete without audit |
| 7 | Record Learning | `record-learning` | At the end | **MEDIUM** — Warning if skipped |

## Critical Rules

- The orchestrator MUST NEVER edit files directly — always delegate
- Every agent runs `bos_select_dna` before starting work (mandatory)
- Every agent runs `bos_run_audit` after completing work (mandatory)
- All quality gates must pass before mission completion
- Governance rules are evaluated BEFORE actions are taken
- Escalate to human for any `critical` risk level action

